title: Economic Effects Of a Transatlantic Free Trade Deal (TTIP)
description:
Please see http://youtu.be/QIYHrFp_EOU for HD Quality!

Who will benefit from a transatlantic free trade deal?

Dr. Ulrich Schoof, Project Manager GED - Global Economic Dynamics, explains the economic effects of the Transatlantic Trade and Investment Partnership (TTIP) between the United States and Europe. The video is based on the latest GED-Study, conducted in partnership with the ifo-Institute, Prof. Gabriel Felbermayer. More information www.ged-shorts.org or www.ged-projects.de.
